{# ── OPERATOR · who you reach (prose + operatorSpec as .incl-card + .checklist). (H2: A Certified ProAdvisor takes the call — and routes you honestly.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="acct-speak-operator" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
